		• Store to HDFS – to be used by various tools such as Hive, Spark, Hbase
		• Store to public cloud such as S3, ADLS, etc.
	Data Processing and Analytics
		• Transforming and combining datasets
		• Creating operational datasets
	Data Scientist Support
		• Data preprocessing for creating AI models
		• Business Intelligence and Visualization
		
